We got to cut it out.

17:44.105 --> 17:45.564
- How old are you?
- Eight.

17:46.482 --> 17:48.942
And he swallowed
something stuck to a fridge.

17:49.068 --> 17:50.527
Darwin says, "Let him die."

17:50.653 --> 17:53.363
If it's already below the stomach,
it should pass on its own.

17:53.489 --> 17:54.364
Strong magnet.

17:54.490 --> 17:55.824
It's messing
with the imaging.

17:55.950 --> 17:58.493
We have no way to...

17:59.287 --> 18:01.413
You got x-ray vision, House?

18:06.294 --> 18:09.421
Whoa, whoa! You're gonna
cut him open? Right here?

18:19.390 --> 18:21.725
It's well into the intestines.
He's fine.

18:22.602 --> 18:24.853
I want my 50 back.

18:25.188 --> 18:26.688
